  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub. Abstract/structural charts only; no\n     readable memory contents shown. Draft until ready. -->\n<p class=\"\">What does an AI agent <em class=\"\">remember</em>, and how is it organized? This takes Coach Artie's accumulated memory, embeds and clusters it, and maps the structure — the cognitive topology of a synthetic mind, visualized.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Cognitive topology — Coach Artie&#x27;s memories embedded and laid out as a map\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/topology.png\" alt=\"Cognitive topology — Coach Artie&#x27;s memories embedded and laid out as a map\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/coachartie-memory/topology.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/coachartie-memory/topology.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/topology.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/coachartie-memory/topology.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Cognitive topology — Coach Artie&#x27;s memories embedded and laid out as a map\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1337\" style=\"--splay-rot:-2.37deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1800×1337\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Hierarchical clustering of the memory space, as a dendrogram\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/hierarchy.png\" alt=\"Hierarchical clustering of the memory space, as a dendrogram\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://re