ory clusters</figcaption></figure></figure></figure>\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/hierarchy.png\" alt=\"Hierarchical clustering of the memory space, as a dendrogram\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/coachartie-memory/hierarchy.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/coachartie-memory/hierarchy.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/hierarchy.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/coachartie-memory/hierarchy.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Hierarchical clustering of the memory space, as a dendrogram\" width=\"1800\" height=\"897\" style=\"--splay-rot:-0.76deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1800×897\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/tsne.png\" alt=\"t-SNE small multiples across the memory clusters\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/coachartie-memory/tsne.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/coachartie-memory/tsne.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/tsne.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/coachartie-memory/tsne.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"t-SNE small multiples across the memory clusters\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1777\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.93deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1800×1777\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay aspect-square w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><p class=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"\">Beyond the static map, the analysis tracks how the memory <em class=\"\">changes</em> — which clusters grow, when memories form, and how the topology shifts over time.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Temporal cluster evolution — how the memory grows and shifts\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/temporal.png\" alt=\"Temporal cluster evolution — how the memory grows and shifts\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/coachartie-memory/temporal.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/coachartie-memory/temporal.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/temporal.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/coachartie-memory/temporal.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Temporal cluster evolution — how the memory grows and shifts\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1116\" style=\"--splay-rot:-1.68deg;\" data-dimensions=\"1800×1116\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Cognitive activity calendar — daily memory-formation patterns\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/coachartie-memory/calendar.png\" alt=\"Cognitive activity calendar — daily memory-formation patterns\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/coachartie-memory/cal